description:
Redevelopment involving: demolition of the existing summerhouse; erection of a part one, part-two-storey plus basement building linked to the east elevation of the existing building (Grade II) in connection with the use of the site as a school; demolition of existing boundary
walls to Broomhouse Lane and Daisy Lane and replacement with new boundary wall; repositioning of vehicular access on Daisy Lane;
associated landscaping, and internal and external alterations.
